<BR>
I think it sucks for clerics. Id rather have a screaming mace, at least that is a light source! When do clerics ever ttack anyway? By the time you get this weapon you should NOT be attacking in fights. If you are, stop playing right now, youll get your group killed.<BR>
<BR>
This weapon is good, but not for clerics.</font></td></tr></table>
